Package com.msgroup.moviesurfer.repositories

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    MovieRepository
    MovieRepository interface manages the Movie entity, extends the JpaRepository and uses it's methods to persist and retrieve Movie objects from the database.
    SeatRepository
    SeatRepository interface manages the Seat entity, extends the JpaRepository and uses * it's methods to persist and retrieve Seat objects from the database.
    UserRepository
    UserRepository interface manages the User entity, extends the CrudRepository and uses it's CRUD methods to persist and retrieve User objects from the database.
